1️⃣ IdentityCertification kya hai?
👉 IdentityCertification = user ke access ka review object
Matlab:-
kisi user ke paas jo access hai
usko review / verify / approve / revoke karna
➡ Ye process IdentityCertification ke through hota hai
✅ Example:-
User: Rahul
Access:-
SAP Write
Admin Role

➡ Manager bole:-
SAP Write ❌ (revoke)
Admin Role ✅ (keep)
👉 Ye pura review = IdentityCertification

🔹 2️⃣ Ye kya karta hai?
👉 Ye manage karta hai:-
access review process
approvals / revocations
compliance tracking

🔹 3️⃣ Kya ye DB me store hota hai?
✅ Haan bhai, DB me store hota hai,
📦 Structure:-
Identity (Rahul)
   ↓
IdentityCertification
   ↓
Items (Role, Entitlement)

🔹 4️⃣ Iske andar kya hota hai?
Field	      Meaning
id:---------certification ID
name:-------certification ka naam
type:-------user / role based
status:-----Pending / Completed
reviewer:---kaun review karega
items:------access items (role, entitlement)
createdDate:----kab start hua
completedDate:--kab finish hua

🔹 5️⃣ Important Methods:-
🔸 Basic:-
getId() → certification ID deta hai
setId(String id) → ID set karta hai
getName() → certification ka naam
setName(String name) → naam set karta hai
getType() → certification type deta hai
setType(String type) → type set karta hai

🔸 Status:-
getStatus() → current status (Pending / Completed)
setStatus(String status) → status set karta hai

🔸 Reviewer:-
getReviewer() → reviewer ka naam deta hai
setReviewer(String reviewer) → reviewer set karta hai

🔸 Items:-
getItems() → access items list deta hai
addItem(Object item) → ek item add karta hai

🔸 Date:-
getCreatedDate() → start date
setCreatedDate(Date date)
getCompletedDate() → end date
setCompletedDate(Date date)

🔸 Utility:-
toString() → readable string
equals(Object obj) → compare karta hai
hashCode() → hash generate karta hai

🚀 🔥 Full Code (SailPointContext ke saath)
import sailpoint.api.SailPointContext;
import sailpoint.api.SailPointFactory;
import sailpoint.object.IdentityCertification;
import java.util.Date;

public class CertificationExample {

    public static void main(String[] args) throws Exception {

        SailPointContext context = SailPointFactory.getCurrentContext();

        IdentityCertification cert = new IdentityCertification();

        // Basic
        cert.setId("CERT101");
        cert.setName("Access Review");
        cert.setType("User");

        // Status
        cert.setStatus("Pending");

        // Reviewer
        cert.setReviewer("Manager");

        // Dates
        cert.setCreatedDate(new Date());

        // Print
        System.out.println(cert.getId());
        System.out.println(cert.getName());
        System.out.println(cert.getStatus());
        System.out.println(cert.getReviewer());

        // Save
        context.saveObject(cert);
        context.commitTransaction();

        System.out.println("✅ Certification Saved");
    }
}
📤 Output:-
CERT101
Access Review
Pending
Manager
✅ Certification Saved